Package UI

Class SuggestionUI

java.lang.Object
UI.UI
UI.SuggestionUI
public class SuggestionUI extends UI
A user interface for handling suggestions related to camps. This class allows students, camp committee members, and staff to submit, manage, and review camp-related suggestions.
